{"tid":458554,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"TVB硬抽《頭條新聞》係違規　通訊局強烈勸諭","createTime":"2017-11-05T03:50:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-05T04:44:52.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"12bceea96baeeab48de5b09af0d9b029f381a8b2","tid":458554,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T03:50:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171105/20204919\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171105%2F20204919&d=e1BInvnWR2pTlA6dXv6sI%2F%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=e859a2e0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171105%2F20204919&h=23f81fa0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171105/20204919</a><br />\n<br />\n【一周必看】<br />\nTVB硬抽《頭條新聞》係違規　通訊局強烈勸諭<br />\n<br />\n港聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n0:00<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無綫電視今年6月30日在未經港台同意下，突然抽起該台節目《頭條新聞》，改播國家主席習近平訪港講話及風水節目；通訊局就事件接獲406宗投訴，早前裁定無綫違反牌照條款，發出強烈勸喻。無綫回應時反批當局漠視特殊情況，稱「難道國家主席首次訪港發言，不比這個節目（《頭條新聞》）重要」。多名民主派議員歡迎裁決，批評無綫擦習近平鞋，令人反感。"},{"pid":"86b3d472b8f44b7b3a92b09606436010e17bcdb4","tid":458554,"uid":114275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T04:41:18.000Z","msg":"無約束力 講完"},{"pid":"bec7e74a9641e02596feed49a5701f0fcaa117a5","tid":458554,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T04:42:29.000Z","msg":"強烈勸喻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7474ace75fff8e97510191e84b09c88ce0c95ce2","tid":458554,"uid":45788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-05T04:44:52.000Z","msg":"[quote]<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171105/20204919\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171105%2F20204919&d=e1BInvnWR2pTlA6dXv6sI%2F%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=e859a2e0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20171105%2F20204919&h=23f81fa0\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20171105/20204919</a><br />\n<br />\n【一周必看】<br />\nTVB硬抽《頭條新聞》係違規　通訊局<span style=\"color: red;\">強烈勸諭</span><br />\n<br />\n有條友搶人野之後你去<span style=\"color: red;\">強烈勸諭</span>個賊就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}